1 subnet = 1 availability zone

default EBS is delete on termination
volume = virtual hard disk
non encrypted by default

security group = virtual firewall
can restrict by IP
stateful - anything you allow in you also allow out

key pair:
public key = padlock
private key = key for padlock

can put public key on multiple servers and use the same private key to open all the padlocks
`ssh ec2-user@54.87.211.0 -i MyEC2KeyPair.pem`

Lab 2:
ec2-54-86-113-103.compute-1.amazonaws.com
